overrides.name: Hunyuan3D v2.1 - Image to 3D
overrides.description: Hunyuan3D V2.1 is a new model that generate a 3D model from a single image in ~5 minutes. It produces higher quality geometry and textures, and it is more robust to different camera angles and object poses.

overrides.name: Hunyuan3D v2 Turbo - Image to 3D
overrides.description: Hunyuan3D V2 Turbo is a new model that generate a 3D model from a single image in ~2.5 minutes. It produces good quality geometry and textures, and it is more robust to different camera angles and object poses.

overrides.name: Hunyuan3D v2 Multi-view - Image to 3D
overrides.description: Hunyuan3D V2 Multi-view is a new model that generate a 3D model from a 4 view images in ~2.5 minutes. It produces higher quality geometry and textures, and it is more robust to different camera angles and object poses.

overrides.name: ElevenLabs - Multilingual v2
